[Dr Bernoth's authoritative comments and updates are very much appreciated.
"OIE Aquatic Manual" is now titled "Manual of Diagnostic Tests for Aquatic
Animals", 2003 <http://oie.int/eng/normes/fmanual/A_summry.htm>. The OIE
Aquatic Animal Health Standards Commission maintains a useful and
recommended website: <http://www.oie.int/fdc/eng/en_fdc.htm>. - Mod.AS]
